WEBVTT

01:40.181 --> 01:41.811
<b>My!</b>

01:42.101 --> 01:45.151
<b>Look at you putting in 
the effort, Yamada-chan.</b>

01:45.441 --> 01:48.401
<b>I need to follow your example.</b>

01:48.401 --> 01:51.491
<b>You already have 
the perfect smile, Ohno-san.</b>

01:51.491 --> 01:52.991
<b>Do I, now?</b>

01:52.991 --> 01:54.411
<b>Yamada.</b>

01:54.821 --> 01:57.781
<b>Can I ask you for a face shot 
and an interview?</b>

01:57.781 --> 02:01.001
<b>What? Corporate PR stuff again?</b>

02:01.001 --> 02:03.161
<b>At least try to hide 
your displeasure, Yamada.</b>

02:03.581 --> 02:06.421
<b>I mean, I just did one not too long ago.</b>

02:06.421 --> 02:08.291
<b>It is what it is.</b>

02:08.291 --> 02:11.341
<b>You're a nominee for 
the Smile Award again this year.</b>

02:11.341 --> 02:12.671
<b>Wow!</b>

02:13.131 --> 02:14.471
<b>Fine.</b>

02:14.471 --> 02:16.681
<b>Let's get it over and done with!</b>

02:17.091 --> 02:19.351
<b>That's some code-switching skill.</b>

02:19.351 --> 02:22.561
<b>I almost miss the zero-smile Yamada 
from your part-time days.</b>

02:25.311 --> 02:28.311
<b></b>8 Years Ago

02:25.311 --> 02:28.311
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

02:29.521 --> 02:30.821
<b>We...</b>

02:30.821 --> 02:32.481
<b>Welcome.</b>

02:32.481 --> 02:33.571
<b>You suck!</b>

02:35.151 --> 02:37.241
<b>What exactly is wrong, Chief?</b>

02:37.241 --> 02:39.871
<b>Your eyes are emotionless, 
your mouth's twitching,</b>

02:39.871 --> 02:40.831
<b>and your voice is too low.</b>

02:40.831 --> 02:44.081
<b>You're making it sound like 
I've got <i>everything</i> wrong.</b>

02:44.081 --> 02:46.331
<b>I'm glad you understand.</b>

02:47.421 --> 02:49.631
<b>How do I teach you to get it right?</b>

02:49.631 --> 02:52.421
<b>Why do you have trouble with this 
when the rest of your work's perfect?</b>

02:52.421 --> 02:54.091
<b>It's hardly perfect.</b>

02:54.631 --> 02:58.051
<b>Not when I get complaints 
about my customer service.</b>

02:59.511 --> 03:02.351
<b>I'm sorry for always causing you trouble.</b>

03:03.721 --> 03:05.561
<b>Listen, Yamada.</b>

03:07.481 --> 03:12.111
<b>The complaints you get are all from 
one customer who's targeting you.</b>

03:12.691 --> 03:16.111
<b>They just want to nitpick the store, 
and they're using you as an excuse.</b>

03:16.611 --> 03:19.991
<b>I'll do something about both that 
and your customer service.</b>

03:20.411 --> 03:22.241
<b>You just keep at it without overthinking.</b>

03:23.831 --> 03:25.001
<b>Okay.</b>

03:25.871 --> 03:27.621
<b><i>The chief is really nice to me.</i></b>

03:28.541 --> 03:32.501
<b><i>Even though I give her so much trouble.</i></b>

03:36.051 --> 03:38.931
<b>If you take this to the service counter,</b>

03:38.931 --> 03:41.181
<b>you can trade it in for a coupon.</b>

03:41.181 --> 03:43.721
<b>Oh, is that how it works?</b>

03:43.721 --> 03:45.641
<b>Thank you, miss.</b>

03:46.601 --> 03:48.391
<b>Thank you for shopping with—</b>

03:53.651 --> 03:54.481
<b>We...</b>

03:57.241 --> 03:58.701
<b>Welcome.</b>

03:59.241 --> 04:00.031
<b>Your point card—</b>

04:00.031 --> 04:03.121
<b>Does it <i>look</i> like I brought it? 
I forgot mine, obviously.</b>

04:04.541 --> 04:05.951
<b>My apologies.</b>

04:06.911 --> 04:09.081
<b>Would you like a bag—</b>

04:09.081 --> 04:11.461
<b>Do you see any in the basket?</b>

04:11.461 --> 04:12.841
<b>That means I need one.</b>

04:13.381 --> 04:17.591
<b>How many times do I need 
to tell you before you learn?</b>

04:18.221 --> 04:20.801
<b>You're absolutely right. I apologize.</b>

04:21.721 --> 04:23.471
<b>I understand.</b>

04:23.471 --> 04:24.601
<b>Hey!</b>

04:24.971 --> 04:28.851
<b>Why would you ring up the eggs first? 
What if they crack at the bottom?!</b>

04:28.851 --> 04:31.271
<b>That's basic common sense!</b>

04:28.851 --> 04:30.731
<b>What's going on there?</b>

04:30.731 --> 04:31.851
<b>That doesn't look good.</b>

04:31.271 --> 04:33.361
<b>Did your superiors teach you nothing?!</b>

04:33.361 --> 04:37.111
<b>Are all the other cashiers like you, too?!</b>

04:37.941 --> 04:39.111
<b>Manager!</b>

04:39.111 --> 04:40.951
<b>Chief Gotou!</b>

04:40.951 --> 04:43.621
<b>That one customer's here again.</b>

04:43.621 --> 04:45.281
<b>Yamada-chan's getting yelled at!</b>

04:46.951 --> 04:50.161
<b>Each and every time, you ring me up 
like you'd rather be anywhere else.</b>

04:50.161 --> 04:53.001
<b>Why do you even work here, girl?!</b>

04:53.001 --> 04:54.711
<b>Don't listen to him.</b>

04:53.331 --> 04:56.881
<b>Why don't you say something? 
Where is your apology?!</b>

04:56.881 --> 04:58.461
<b>My apologies.</b>

04:58.461 --> 04:59.631
<b>Not this again!</b>

05:00.051 --> 05:03.261
<b>At least apologize like you mean it!</b>

05:03.261 --> 05:05.891
<b>This is why I hate student 
part-timers serving me!</b>

05:05.891 --> 05:08.431
<b>The one at the convenience 
store next door sucked, too,</b>

05:08.431 --> 05:10.561
<b>but you're even worse!</b>

05:10.561 --> 05:13.651
<b>I try to tell you how to do things, 
but you can't be bothered—</b>

05:13.651 --> 05:14.771
<b>Hey.</b>

05:16.361 --> 05:17.781
<b>Excuse me.</b>

05:21.201 --> 05:22.741
<b>Can you stop talking?</b>

05:24.821 --> 05:27.241
<b>Wha... What's that supposed to mean?</b>

05:27.241 --> 05:30.121
<b>Can't you see I'm scolding 
an incompetent cashier?!</b>

05:30.121 --> 05:31.291
<b>Oh, uh...</b>

05:31.581 --> 05:35.001
<b>Yeah, I heard that loud and clear,</b>

05:35.001 --> 05:39.341
<b>but you started bringing up 
irrelevant crap midway.</b>

05:39.801 --> 05:43.431
<b>Also, aren't you always here 
yelling at this girl?</b>

05:45.261 --> 05:47.551
<b>Could you give it a rest already?</b>

05:48.181 --> 05:50.851
<b>There are other registers here,</b>

05:48.851 --> 05:50.851
<b>Go, big guy!</b>

05:51.981 --> 05:53.941
<b>so why do you go out of your way...</b>

05:56.111 --> 05:58.651
<b>to do this every time I'm next in line?</b>

06:03.531 --> 06:06.701
<b>Sir, could you come with us, please?</b>

06:07.121 --> 06:07.911
<b>Tch.</b>

06:10.951 --> 06:12.581
<b>Let Ohno-san take over.</b>

06:13.621 --> 06:16.751
<b>You take a break, okay, dear?</b>

06:19.671 --> 06:20.711
<b>Okay.</b>

06:30.721 --> 06:32.601
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:32.601 --> 06:33.231
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:33.231 --> 06:33.981
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:33.981 --> 06:35.021
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:35.021 --> 06:35.481
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:35.481 --> 06:37.481
<b>Superfresh Market</b>

06:45.531 --> 06:46.531
<b>Um...</b>

06:47.871 --> 06:50.031
<b>Oh, hey, it's you.</b>

06:50.031 --> 06:53.751
<b>Thank you for stepping in 
to help me back there.</b>

06:54.161 --> 06:57.331
<b>Also, I'm sorry you've had to wait 
because of me multiple times.</b>

06:57.331 --> 06:59.211
<b>Hey, wait, no.</b>

06:59.211 --> 07:02.251
<b>It's not like that was all your fault.</b>

07:02.841 --> 07:05.671
<b>No, it <i>is</i> all my fault 
for sucking at customer service.</b>

07:05.671 --> 07:07.551
<b>So I'm sorry.</b>

07:12.101 --> 07:16.391
<b>See, I didn't do that 
to help you out or anything.</b>

07:18.311 --> 07:24.531
<b>I was just cranky because something 
godawful happened at work today,</b>

07:24.941 --> 07:28.111
<b>and then I saw you 
getting yelled at again.</b>

07:32.991 --> 07:37.661
<b>It was like, even the cashier who's 
always good to me couldn't catch a break.</b>

07:38.171 --> 07:40.461
<b>And that ticked me off, 
which is why I stepped in.</b>

07:40.921 --> 07:42.211
<b>I'm good to you?</b>

07:42.751 --> 07:45.591
<b>You are. You're quick and thorough.</b>

07:46.221 --> 07:49.301
<b>You'd say that to a rude part-timer 
who doesn't even care?</b>

07:50.391 --> 07:51.801
<b>You don't care?</b>

07:52.391 --> 07:54.811
<b>When you're always giving 100 percent?</b>

07:57.181 --> 07:59.561
<b><u>Always start with a smile</u></b>

08:00.401 --> 08:03.071
<b><i>I have to work fast, if nothing else.</i></b>

08:09.401 --> 08:11.491
<b><i>Why can't I do it right?</i></b>

08:16.791 --> 08:18.831
<b>Wait, are you...</b>

08:21.961 --> 08:25.381
<b>S-Sorry, did I say something 
to make you cry?</b>

08:25.381 --> 08:26.711
<b>I'm not crying.</b>

08:26.711 --> 08:29.841
<b>I'm just sweating from my eyes.</b>

08:29.841 --> 08:30.971
<b>Sweat...?</b>

08:31.301 --> 08:35.761
<b>How can you tell I'm always 
giving 100 percent?</b>

08:35.761 --> 08:38.181
<b>My customer service is so bad,</b>

08:39.181 --> 08:42.731
<b>I get targeted by a troublesome customer</b>

08:43.441 --> 08:46.401
<b>and cause my coworkers 
and the chief so much trouble...</b>

08:49.031 --> 08:53.161
<b>I want to fix this! I love this job!</b>

08:53.741 --> 08:54.491
<b>This sucks...</b>

08:57.621 --> 08:59.831
<b>You love this job, do you?</b>

09:03.921 --> 09:05.671
<b>Then you'll be fine.</b>

09:09.261 --> 09:12.091
<b>Keep doing something because you love it,</b>

09:12.091 --> 09:16.761
<b>and everything else you need 
will surely follow.</b>

09:29.231 --> 09:31.321
<b>Huh? A-Are you okay?</b>

09:31.321 --> 09:32.531
<b>It's that.</b>

09:32.901 --> 09:35.821
<b>Your cigarette smoke got into my eyes.</b>

09:35.821 --> 09:37.531
<b>S-Sorry! I brought it too close!</b>

09:37.531 --> 09:38.491
<b>Pfft.</b>

09:39.041 --> 09:40.411
<b>Wait, what is it now?</b>

09:40.411 --> 09:41.541
<b>Are you okay?</b>

09:42.211 --> 09:45.881
<b>All your reactions are so over the top.</b>

09:54.841 --> 09:57.851
<b>Okay, that should do it.</b>

09:57.851 --> 09:59.311
<b>Interview done.</b>

09:59.641 --> 10:01.601
<b>You can take your break now.</b>

10:01.601 --> 10:03.271
<b>Hey, boss?</b>

10:04.521 --> 10:06.981
<b>Back when this store had a different name,</b>

10:06.981 --> 10:10.571
<b>there was a guy who snapped at 
a customer who had it out for me.</b>

10:10.571 --> 10:11.691
<b>Remember him?</b>

10:11.691 --> 10:17.201
<b>Huh? Do you have any idea how many 
of those I've seen in all my years here?</b>

10:17.201 --> 10:19.161
<b>Not a chance. 
I don't remember that at all.</b>

10:20.831 --> 10:23.831
<b><i>Well, even I don't remember his face.</i></b>

10:25.251 --> 10:29.341
<b><i>He always smoked by the entrance 
after shopping with us.</i></b>

10:30.211 --> 10:33.131
<b><i>He was a man with 
ruffled hair, battered shirts,</i></b>

10:33.131 --> 10:35.431
<b><i>and awful bags under his eyes.</i></b>

10:40.431 --> 10:45.731
<b><i>He stopped showing up after we 
removed that ashtray due to a complaint.</i></b>

10:48.361 --> 10:52.111
<b><i>I wonder if he's still 
smoking somewhere else.</i></b>

11:02.571 --> 11:06.201
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

11:06.701 --> 11:10.331
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

11:11.041 --> 11:14.291
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
